CityFed Financial Corp. said@#%^&*1
it expects to report a loss of at least $125 million to $150 million for the third quarter.@#%^&*1
In the year-earlier period, CityFed had net income of $485,000, but no per-share earnings.@#%^&*2
CityFed's president and chief executive officer, John Atherton, said@#%^&*3
the loss stems from several factors.@#%^&*3
He said@#%^&*4
nonperforming assets rose to slightly more than $700 million from $516 million between June and September.@#%^&*4
