Accordingly, CityFed estimated@#%^&*6
that it will provide between $85 million and $110 million for credit losses in the third quarter.@#%^&*6
CityFed added@#%^&*7
that significant additional loan-loss provisions may be required by federal regulators as part of the current annual examination of City Federal Savings Bank, CityFed's primary subsidiary,@#%^&*7
based in Somerset, N.J.@#%^&*7
